      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW BASTOW (1) could manage only third at Traralgon last time but turned heads when clocking a speedy 22.17 over 390m at Warrnambool the start prior. Rates a top chance if runs up to time two back. LAKEVIEW MITCH (7) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish third (22.39) at this track in a Grade 5 over 390m. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Will give a great sight again. PAW XANTHIE (6) doesn't win out of turn but looks close to breaking through. Finished third (22.29) at Ballarat last time making it two minors on end. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and two minor placings. Leading player again. SWEET I AM (2) is in the mix despite missing out at this track last time.",
